Class BoardTreeNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • models.GenericNode
      • models.BoardTreeNode

  • public class BoardTreeNode
extends GenericNode
    Board Node. Represents node which values are boards. Destined to be used in a 15-puzzle solution. Extends GenericNode. A fitness value of the board inside is added. Furthemore, a movement indicates the move into the puzzle to reach the actual node from the parent.
